{"tid":1025603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣諗住係香港唔買樓唔結婚生仔","createTime":"2019-02-17T12:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T13:59:08.000Z","uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebfff7e5695fe2eda5fad1ac5abe7c11c87a0310","tid":1025603,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"老母個邊係外國一早起左間屋留左個位俾我<br />\n年紀輕輕已經諗住到時退休返去等死<br />\n有埋祖墳俾我瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係香港樓又買唔到又要俾班支那人污染<br />\n除左係香港賺個夠本之外已經無咩好留戀<br />\n雖然我好鐘意香港<br />\n但係睇住班支那人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422339fcfdd9f7cfe8d201564143a9d9f9890495","tid":1025603,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"係全世界任何一個地方都唔應該買樓生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d85be7efb8506f5d2b0cedec84db9ec0917f5d","tid":1025603,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:03:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1a027b4c2ba960de67a319136e35623d4f0cd25","tid":1025603,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"樓主依家可以去訓祖墳"}]}